seo: 天问物业ERP系统,任意文件读取漏洞,信息泄露,OwnerVacantDownLoad.aspx
seo_en: Tianwen Property ERP System, Arbitrary File Read Vulnerability, Information Leakage, OwnerVacantDownLoad.aspx
summary: 检测天问物业ERP系统中OwnerVacantDownLoad.aspx接口存在的任意文件读取漏洞，该漏洞可能导致系统内部配置文件被未授权访问，造成敏感信息泄露。
summary_en: Detect the arbitrary file read vulnerability in the OwnerVacantDownLoad.aspx interface of Tianwen Property ERP System. This vulnerability may allow unauthorized access to internal configuration files, leading to sensitive information leakage.
